      "description": "Looking for an affordable ride or a hands-on project? This vehicle is priced to move and could be just the opportunity you've been waiting for! We'll be straight with you \u2014 the car is in poor condition, showing significant wear inside and out, and will likely need some mechanical attention and cosmetic work. That said, it's a real car at a real bargain price, perfect for a mechanically inclined buyer or someone who just needs basic transportation on a tight budget. Come take a look and see if it's the right fit for you!",
