      "description": "Looking for an ultra-budget ride to get you from A to B? This car is priced to move and offers real value for the savvy buyer! We want to be upfront \u2014 this vehicle shows significant wear, has mechanical issues that will need attention, and is best suited for someone comfortable with a project car or basic transportation needs. If you're handy with repairs or just need something affordable to work with, this could be your opportunity!",
