      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Ready to hit the road and turn heads! This vehicle is in good condition \u2014 it runs smoothly, handles with confidence, and has clearly been well looked after. You'll find only minor cosmetic blemishes here and there, nothing that takes away from the overall appeal. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a weekend adventure, this car is a reliable companion that won't let you down. A fantastic opportunity to get into a well-maintained vehicle at a fair price!",
      "price": 34000.0,
